#ANIMATION 6
#phrase Rick  1
If I were to choose a new place to live, the Khadaganian Empire would be the last choice. The state is founded on brute force and every Khadaganian is a master of those below him and a slave of those above him.
#CAMERA 11
#ANIMATION 6
#phrase Rick  2
But even the highest-ranking Khadaganian citizens are slaves to Emperor Neseb, a powerful Magician who has managed to concentrate more power in his hands than any other monarch before him. And though Suslanger is considered to be the Empire's backyard, you are going to find it very, very difficult - even there.
